    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/5489afd95bfb816971f417e73124771d.poster.avif?t=1767977230\" width=626 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/5489afd95bfb816971f417e73124771d.webm?t=1767977230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/5489afd95bfb816971f417e73124771d.mp4?t=1767977230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这一次让我们在<strong>《一起开火车2：汽笛重鸣》</strong>中将手忙脚乱进行到底！多人铁轨建造NO！好友在线拆台YES！在这个全新世界中，伴随着火车前行铺设铁轨；这一次，自由度超过你的想象。随机应变见缝插针就是通关秘笈，快清理掉那个挡路的障碍物，再不清理火车就要……脱轨报废啦！<br><br><strong>你的旅途越来越美好</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/6c40888c6911984d27163d9fb13e099a.poster.avif?t=1767977230\" width=626 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/6c40888c6911984d27163d9fb13e099a.webm?t=1767977230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/6c40888c6911984d27163d9fb13e099a.mp4?t=1767977230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>和队友的每一次旅行，都有可能带来新的奖励和更多永久升级！解锁改变游戏玩法的新角色、新引擎、新车厢和其他拓展内容；发挥你的创意创造出无数种独特的火车配置。损失掉火车头也别灰心……重回正轨让汽笛重鸣才是轨道之行的乐趣所在！<br><br><strong>选择你的轨道</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/b444fa1e170c56b33df4e95da88b3e25.poster.avif?t=1767977230\" width=626 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/b444fa1e170c56b33df4e95da88b3e25.webm?t=1767977230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/b444fa1e170c56b33df4e95da88b3e25.mp4?t=1767977230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>横跨不同环境场景的剧情，更多可选的分支路线，保证让你每场游戏都有独特体验。快速适应这些新的兴趣点、支线任务、Boss战和随机挑战，享受更多乐趣！当然我们也提供了更多可解锁的外观物品，让你的角色与众不同！<br><br><strong>与社区一起创造、分享、游玩</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/364b5a2b5b8d4d5e00fa9e17ea9ed4de.poster.avif?t=1767977230\" width=626 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/364b5a2b5b8d4d5e00fa9e17ea9ed4de.webm?t=1767977230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/364b5a2b5b8d4d5e00fa9e17ea9ed4de.mp4?t=1767977230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在关卡编辑器中尽情发挥你无穷的想象力，自定义地图并分享到Unrailed社区。开发团队感谢并将极力推荐其中的优秀作品。不擅长创造也没关系，相信在浏览尝试其他玩家的创意关卡时，你能收获更多手忙脚乱的乐趣！<br><br><strong>有合作也有对抗</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/fa79c6a1d0ffc4e5663c9a4b2b3b9096.poster.avif?t=1767977230\" width=626 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/fa79c6a1d0ffc4e5663c9a4b2b3b9096.webm?t=1767977230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211170/extras/fa79c6a1d0ffc4e5663c9a4b2b3b9096.mp4?t=1767977230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在全新的8人对战模式中，燃烧斗志与求胜心，与其他队伍激烈对抗。动作回放以检验团队实力，冲击在线排行榜看看谁将赢得最高分！",
